  "title": "Famous European Routes | 5 Spectacular Train Trips",
  "excerpt": "Train travels have their charm, especially when you have the opportunity that from its windows to observe the most beautiful sights of Europe. Here are some worldwide famous itineraries for lovers of European railways",
